1
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,680
Du Long

2
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,640
I am Du Long

3
00:01:26,800 --> 00:01:29,320
I admit the severed hand murders were all my doing

4
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:30,600
They had nothing to do with anyone else

5
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,120
I stayed with the Wang family for many years

6
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,520
On the surface, I was their steward

7
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:39,240
But they treated me like a dog

8
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,960
Steward Du, I heard you're sick

9
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,840
I made you some soup. Drink it while it's hot

10
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:48,200
You must be feeling awful

11
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:48,880
Have a piece of candy

12
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,560
You'll be better soon

13
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,520
Only Shuang'er and her mother

14
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,760
ever treated me with sincerity

15
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:57,440
But the Wang family, for that monster's sake

16
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,960
caused the deaths of the mother and daughter

17
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,720
and even smeared their names

18
00:02:01,040 --> 00:02:02,440
not letting them rest in peace

19
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:06,360
I will win justice for them

20
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,680
That ungrateful wretch

21
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,520
Carry him away

22
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,920
Don't let his bad luck rub off on me

23
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:32,800
Mr. Zheng, you found the real killer for me

24
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,800
You've worked hard for this

25
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,160
You're too kind, Master Wang

26
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:41,000
I'll have the servants send your payment at once

27
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:44,480
As for what this letter says, it's utter nonsense

28
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,480
There's no need to take it seriously

29
00:02:46,440 --> 00:02:48,400
Now that the case has been solved

30
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,840
it was no vengeful spirit taking lives

31
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:51,960
then let the bone collecting end here

32
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,880
Take care, you two. I won't see you out

33
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,800
But the Wang family, for that monster's sake

34
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,280
caused the deaths of the mother and daughter

35
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:28,080
That thing that attacked us

36
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,880
was it human or a ghost?

37
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,520
Hasn't this case already been solved?

38
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,120
Why are we still investigating the Wangs?

39
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,240
Not even close

40
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:41,120
The chief culprit back then was Wang Shengchang

41
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:44,160
Do you think the killer would spare him so easily?

42
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:49,640
Besides, for a case this meticulous

43
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,560
one person couldn't have done it alone

44
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,960
You mean he had an accomplice?

45
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,840
Right, there's one more thing

46
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,800
The Wang family really is keeping something

47
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:05,120
Xunan and I have already been attacked by it twice

48
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,680
Du Long mentioned it too

49
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:09,360
Exactly, I told you the Wang family is haunted

50
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,760
You finally believe me now, don't you?

51
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,840
I looked into it as you asked

52
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,360
The circled spots on this map all belong to the Wangs

53
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,600
Every other place looks normal

54
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,520
Except this one

55
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,720
This is just a wasteland

56
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:30,200
Why do you think the Wangs bought an abandoned house

57
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,400
like this?

58
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:33,600
This place is so remote

59
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,440
No one can live here

60
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,520
and it can't make money

61
00:04:35,520 --> 00:04:37,040
What else could it be for?

62
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,720
Don't you think this is the perfect place to hide things?

63
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,040
There's not a soul in sight

64
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,120
What is that stench?

65
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,320
Could they be keeping livestock here?

66
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:05,360
You're right

67
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:08,040
But it's no livestock

68
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,440
It's some kind of monster I've never seen

69
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,200
Keep searching

70
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:15,440
All right

71
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,240
This is Master's Bone staff

72
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:32,000
It symbolizes the Bone Collector's identity

73
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,560
Master would never discard it carelessly

74
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:37,640
Go, hurry, hurry, hide

75
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,120
Run

76
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,560
Run

77
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:57,280
What the hell? That nearly killed me

78
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,600
Are you all right?

79
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,480
I'm fine

80
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,800
What?

81
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,680
He actually didn't die

82
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,880
This Zheng Yu really is hard to deal with

83
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:19,520
Only two months remain until Sacrifice Day

84
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:24,000
There must not be a single mistake before then

85
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,200
What about that thing?

86
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:32,800
I'll take that thing away for now until things cool down

87
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:33,880
Remember

88
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,880
Keep a close watch on Zhao Xunan

89
00:06:37,320 --> 00:06:39,960
She is the key to Sacrifice Day

90
00:06:43,840 --> 00:06:44,960
May the Bodhisattva bless us

91
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,000
and let the Fox Spirit leave at once

92
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:49,040
and stop clinging to our mistress

93
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,320
Amitabha

94
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:52,560
Third Concubine

95
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,520
The master has arrived

96
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,600
Master

97
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,320
Now the First Madame has gone mad

98
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,680
The eldest young master is ill too

99
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:07,640
The safety of all in the Lu family depends on you

100
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,280
Madam, do not panic

101
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:14,320
I shall dispel evil for the Lu matriarch at once

102
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,600
Master, look

103
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,840
This Fox Spirit has great Spiritual Power indeed

104
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,520
To dispel this Fox Spirit's resentment

105
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,760
I fear the Merit I've built up over the years

106
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,160
will all be spent up

107
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,760
As long as the First Madame can be saved

108
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:40,600
money is not the problem

109
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,000
Supreme Primordial One

110
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,280
command the spirit hosts

111
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:56,680
guard the mortal soil

112
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:58,200
preserve the vital essence

113
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:12,960
Hold her down
